either one is nice, just don't waste gold upgrading {{item:3303}} 

if you're in a lane matchup where u can get alot of autos off on lane opponents get {{item:3303}} 
if you're in somewhat of a passive lane where you can't or value the sustain higher, get {{item:3301}} 

in either case make sure to stock up on plenty of {{item:2010}}  for sustaining your lane!
